transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hey, thanks for calling Viber, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, my name is Peter Little.

Speaker 1: And I ordered your product, I think it was last month.

Speaker 2: And I paid for it, and I got something in the mail last week that's saying stuff.

Speaker 1: And I'm trying to figure out, do you all send stuff to people that they don't order?

Speaker 2: Oh, I get what you're saying, you got an order you weren't expecting.

Speaker 1: Yeah, so it looks like you got set up on our VIP prescription there, Mr. Little.

Speaker 2: I can pause that service for you if you didn't want to get the orders automatically or anything like that.

Speaker 1: No, I never ask for it automatically.

Speaker 2: Each time I've called in, I ask for it and they send it.

Speaker 1: Yeah, it looks like they set you up on our VIP prescription the last time you called in

Speaker 2: to get the order at like a cheap rate, and next time they set you up to get one two months later,

Speaker 1: which was the one you just recently got.

Speaker 2: Okay, and there's something else that I talked to somebody before about.

Speaker 1: They want to play games with my name.

Speaker 2: My name is Peter Little, not Little Peter, okay?

Speaker 1: So I want that fixed on the outside label.

Speaker 2: Can you do that?

Speaker 1: Yeah, no, so it shouldn't be that.

Speaker 2: I'll make sure that it's not that, Mr. Little.

Speaker 1: I have it here as Peter Little, so that's what you should see.

Speaker 2: Yeah, this is legitimate mail, so yeah, I'll reach out to them and tell them that for sure.

Speaker 1: So you definitely shouldn't see that happen again.

Speaker 2: So, again, I don't want to receive something they don't ask for.

Speaker 1: Okay, yeah, like I said, I can pause this account for you, Mr. Little, up to six months at a time.

Speaker 2: You can call us any time before then if you need anything.

Speaker 1: Okay, thanks.

Speaker 2: Okay, no problem. You're all set then, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
